{"build_type":"library","description":"As-completed dispatch: drains the item queue, spawning one publishing worker-runner thread per pending work item. Context prctx is 56 bytes (7 slots): [0..4] worker/publish fields, [6] per-thread arena block carved by provision-worker-arena-block-into-region (de-globalization). Advances head and launched count; recurses until head reaches the queue tail. Slice 4.4b-1: prctx and stack now come from grab-released-or-fresh-arena-chunk (16-byte grab header, so the reaper's region-16/stack-16 push is valid), the stack BASE is recorded in block[81] (byte648), and the worker's prctx is registered in the block-ring state[10] at its spawn slot (head_slot / rk_slot) with a non-null-slot fault guard, so the collector can reap it on the gone-edge.","module_name":"dispatch-pending-work-items-spawning-worker-runners","package_name":"dispatch-pending-work-items-spawning-worker-runners","function_definitions":{"dispatch-pending-work-items-spawning-worker-runners":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"state","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"head_slot","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i81","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":81},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i10","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":10},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"rk_slot","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"ring_mask","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4095},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":